[l] Old and busted: Das Internet verroht die Sitten.New hotness: Parents are worried the Amazon Echo is conditioning their kids to be rude.“I’ve found my kids pushing the virtual assistant further than they would push a human,” says Avi Greengart, a tech analyst and father of five who lives in Teaneck, New Jersey. “[Alexa] never says ‘That was rude’ or ‘I’m tired of you asking me the same question over and over again.'”
